{Speech 3 Answer 6*}{}{My right arm looks like a piece of crap.}
{Speech 3 Answer 6**}{}{Neither of my arms works.}
{Speech 3 Answer 6***}{}{I can't put weight on my left leg.}
{Speech 3 Answer 6****}{}{I've got trouble with my right leg.}
{Speech 3 Answer 7}{}{Doctor, I can't walk!}
