{Speech 19 Answer 20}{}{Oh, doc, you remember my name? You've got a good memory!}
{Speech 19 Answer 16}{}{Remind me, what is it you do here?}
{Speech 19 Answer 3}{}{Doctor, I need medical help.}
{Speech 19 Answer 9}{}{I want to buy some medicine.}
{Speech 19 Answer Exit}{}{Help yourself, I'm fine.}
{Speech 19 Answer Exit*}{}{Help yourself, I'm fine.}
{Speech 19 Answer Exit**}{}{Nothing, thanks.}
