{Speech 20 Answer 9}{}{Oh! Can I buy some of those magic potions from you?}
{Speech 20 Answer Exit*}{}{Mmm. I see. I have to go.}
{Speech 21}{}{Hello. [Looks at you closely] Oooh. I'm a doctor. Doc-tor. Know how to heal. How can I help you? Just don't make noise, or I'll send you off to the shaman for healing.}
{Speech 21 Answer 26}{}{Doc, it hurts.}
{Speech 21 Answer 9}{}{Doc, sell me some powders.}
{Speech 21 Answer 22}{}{Doc, tell me a story.}
{Speech 21 Answer 24}{}{Uuu. Ugh.}
{Speech 21 Answer 25}{}{AAAA! Aaaa! Aaaa! A!}
{Speech 21 Answer 25*}{}{AAAA! Aaaa! Aaaa! A!}
{Speech 22}{}{Once upon a time an Eye was crawling across the Wasteland. And toward it came a Leg. The Eye says: "Leg, let's travel together?" The Leg answers: "Let's." The Eye climbed onto the Leg, and they set off traveling. Now the Eye doesn't have to crawl, and the Leg can see where it's going. ...it's not funny, but at least it's about medicine.}
{Speech 22 Answer 23}{}{Doc, tell me another!}
{Speech 22 Answer Exit}{}{Thanks!}
{Speech 23}{}{That's it, the stories are over. So do you need help with anything?}
{Speech 23 Answer 26}{}{Doc, it hurts here.}
{Speech 23 Answer 9}{}{Doc, sell me some powders.}
{Speech 23 Answer Exit}{}{Nah. Thanks for the story!}
{Speech 24}{}{Well, if you don't need anything, we'll wrap it up for today.}
{Speech 25}{}{...}
{Speech 26}{}{Mmm, what's wrong, my dear?}
{Speech 26 Answer 34}{}{Arm.}
{Speech 26 Answer 34*}{}{Arms...}
{Speech 26 Answer 34**}{}{Leg.}
{Speech 26 Answer 34***}{}{Legs...}
{Speech 26 Answer 34****}{}{Eye.}
{Speech 26 Answer 30}{}{Me feel sick... From scorpion.}
{Speech 26 Answer 31}{}{Me jump in green puddle... Now no hair and skin coming off.}
{Speech 26 Answer 27}{}{Doc, me eat lots powder and breathe to get stronger, now me have nothing, and want to scratch out own eyes...}
{Speech 26 Answer 32}{}{I'm all covered in blood.}
{Speech 26 Answer 25}{}{Nothing! Hee-hee.}
{Speech 27}{}{Mmm. I'm ashamed to ask you this, but to heal you I'll need to spend 900 coins on medicine. And you have to pay it yourself.}
{Speech 27 Answer 28}{}{What?! Have you lost your mind, you old codger?}
{Speech 27 Answer Exit}{}{Doc, too much. Me come back later.}
{Speech 27 Answer 29}{}{Ugh. Fine!}
{Speech 27 Answer Exit*}{}{Nah. Easier for me to just gorge myself again.}
{Speech 28}{}{Bye, faker.}
{Speech 29}{}{So... Eat this powder... And this little pill... And wash it down with water. There. Done, it'll ease up soon.}
{Speech 29 Answer Exit}{}{Thanks!}
{Speech 29 Answer Exit*}{}{900 coins...}
{Speech 30}{}{Here, drink this.}
{Speech 30 Answer Exit}{}{Thanks!}
{Speech 31}{}{Let's give you a little shot... Done.}
{Speech 32}{}{See that pretty girl standing there? That's Francesca. Go to her, she'll bandage you up.}
{Speech 32 Answer Exit}{}{Thanks!}
{Speech 32 Answer 33}{}{Doc, how much gold you take?}
{Speech 33}{}{Nothing at all, we don't take money from those in need.}
{Speech 34}{}{Ooh, that's serious. Go into that little room there, see my assistant Rachel. She'll put everything back the way it was.}
{Speech 34 Answer Exit}{}{Thanks!}
{Speech 34 Answer 33}{}{Doc, how much gold you take?}
{Speech 35}{}{Sorry, my assistant was killed, I can't help you right now. We have to wait until she comes back. Ugh, how fast times change... She'll come back from the other world. Five years ago a phrase like that would have scared me to death. So, there it is. Sorry.}
