{Speech 35 Answer 9*}{}{Doc, at least sell powders...}
{Speech 35 Answer Exit}{}{Oh, damn. Well, let's hope she comes back soon.}
{Speech 35 Answer Exit*}{}{Me go to shaman!}
{Speech 35 Answer 36}{}{Well, thanks, doctor. By the time she comes back, I'll have already headed there myself...}
{Speech 36}{}{In the canyon west of here lives a shaman... I recommend him.}
